# PocketShift Project Conventions

## API Layer

- All mutation functions in `src/lib/api/*.ts` use `withOfflineMutation()`
- Return type: `Promise<void | { queued: true }>`
- Mutation handlers must check `isOfflineQueued(data)` and skip query invalidation when queued

## Components

- Use shadcn/ui primitives from `@/components/ui/`
- Shared components: `EmptyState`, `QueryError`, `ConfirmDeleteDialog`, `OfflineBanner`
- Page-specific UI can live in page files; extract to `components/` when reused

## Styling

- Tailwind CSS; prefer `cn()` utility for conditional classes
- Follow existing patterns for cards, dialogs, forms

## Validation

- Zod schemas in `src/lib/validations.ts`
- Use `schema.safeParse()` before submitting forms

## Error Handling

- Use `formatError()` from `lib/error-utils.ts` for user-facing messages
- Error boundaries on app and auth layouts
- `QueryError` for query failures; show retry option
